on class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto py-20 px-6\"><div class=\"text-center mb-16\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900\">Our Service Offerings</h2><p class=\"text-slate-600 mt-3 max-w-2xl mx-auto\">From satellite TV installation to CCTV and Starlink setup, we cover every step with accredited workmanship, genuine equipment, and friendly support.</p></div><div class=\"grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3\"><article class=\"rounded-3xl bg-white p-8 shadow-xl border border-slate-100 transition hover:-translate-y-1\"><div class=\"mb-6\"><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Satellite TV Installation</h3><p class=\"text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed\">Accredited installation and setup for Dstv, Zuku, Startimes, Gotv, and Azam. Enjoy clear signal and expert support.</p></div><div class=\"space-y-3 mb-6\"><p class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-500 text-sm\"><span class=\"mt-1 inline-flex h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-blue-600\"></span>Dish &amp; decoder setup</p><p class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-500 text-sm\"><span class=\"mt-1 inline-flex h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-blue-600\"></span>Xtraview &amp; extra TV points</p><p class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-500 text-sm\"><span class=\"mt-1 inline-flex h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-blue-600\"></span>Signal repair &amp; realignment</p></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-[0.18em]\">Starting at</span><span class=\"text-xl font-extrabold text-blue-600\">Kes 1,500</span></div></article><article class=\"rounded-3xl bg-white p-8 shadow-xl border border-slate-100 transition hover:-translate-y-1\"><div class=\"mb-6\"><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">TV Wall Mounting</h3><p class=\"text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed\">Professional mounting for all TV sizes with tilt, swivel, or ceiling brackets. Clean finish and secure installation.</p></div><div class=\"space-y-3 mb-6\"><p class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-500 text-sm\"><span class=\"mt-1 inline-flex h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-blue-600\"></span>Swivel &amp; tilt brackets</p><p class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-500 text-sm\"><span class=\"mt-1 inline-flex h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-blue-600\"></span>Cable management</p><p class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-500 text-sm\"><span class=\"mt-1 inline-flex h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-blue-600\"></span>Sound bar &amp; home theater setup</p></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-[0.18em]\">Starting at</span><span class=\"text-xl font-extrabold text-blue-600\">Kes 1,500</span></div></article><article class=\"rounded-3xl bg-white p-8 shadow-xl border border-slate-100 transition hover:-translate-y-1\"><div class=\"mb-6\"><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Starlink Internet Setup</h3><p class=\"text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed\">Get high-speed Starlink internet professionally installed for homes and businesses. Fast, reliable, and secure.</p></div><div class=\"space-y-3 mb-6\"><p class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-500 text-sm\"><span class=\"mt-1 inline-flex h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-blue-600\"></span>Mounting &amp; alignment</p><p class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-500 text-sm\"><span class=\"mt-1 inline-flex h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-blue-600\"></span>Router configuration</p><p class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-500 text-sm\"><span class=\"mt-1 inline-flex h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-blue-600\"></span>Signal optimization</p></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-[0.18em]\">Starting at</span><span class=\"text-xl font-extrabold text-blue-600\">Kes 4,000</span></div></article><article class=\"rounded-3xl bg-white p-8 shadow-xl border border-slate-100 transition hover:-translate-y-1\"><div class=\"mb-6\"><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">CCTV &amp; Security Systems</h3><p class=\"text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed\">Secure your home or business with CCTV cameras, electric fences, and alarm systems. Remote monitoring available.</p></div><div class=\"space-y-3 mb-6\"><p class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-500 text-sm\"><span class=\"mt-1 inline-flex h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-blue-600\"></span>Camera installation &amp; servicing</p><p class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-500 text-sm\"><span class=\"mt-1 inline-flex h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-blue-600\"></span>Electric fence setup</p><p class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-500 text-sm\"><span class=\"mt-1 inline-flex h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-blue-600\"></span>Home security systems</p></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-[0.18em]\">Starting at</span><span class=\"text-xl font-extrabold text-blue-600\">Kes 5,000</span></div></article><article class=\"rounded-3xl bg-white p-8 shadow-xl border border-slate-100 transition hover:-translate-y-1\"><div class=\"mb-6\"><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">Central Dish &amp; Aerial</h3><p class=\"text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed\">Centralized dish and aerial installations for apartments and estates. Clean, efficient, and cost-effective solutions.</p></div><div class=\"space-y-3 mb-6\"><p class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-500 text-sm\"><span class=\"mt-1 inline-flex h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-blue-600\"></span>Shared dish systems</p><p class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-500 text-sm\"><span class=\"mt-1 inline-flex h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-blue-600\"></span>Apartment cabling</p><p class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-500 text-sm\"><span class=\"mt-1 inline-flex h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-blue-600\"></span>Maintenance &amp; support</p></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-[0.18em]\"